Package: DiagROC
Type: Package
Title: ROC Analysis with Diagnostic Accuracy Tools
Version: 0.9.4
Author: İbrahim Altunok
Maintainer: İbrahim Altunok <ibrahim@altunok.md>
Description: A module for ROC analysis extended with diagnostic accuracy metrics. 
  This module allows users to perform one or more ROC analyses along with diagnostic
  accuracy assessments using the optimal threshold based on Youden's Index. It
  also enables the selection of one or more custom coordinate points for a
  variable, and includes a comprehensive manual calculator. For detailed information, 
  feature requests or reporting bugs, please visit the project's <a
  href="https://github.com/altunokmd/DiagROC" target="_blank">GitHub
  Repository</a>
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: jmvcore (>= 0.8.5), R6, pROC, ggplot2
